    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, why did you mention \"Goblin's Greed\"? I don't get the reference. Can you just stick to the actual legal/financial explanation of how the money is released? I'm a bit confused about the mechanics of it.",
      "source": "evaluator"
